task.summary: Default task
- New features: Add "user-settings" and transfer info-editing into the new "user-info". - Update "userNavBar".
Resolve non-merged DataBase.
Add more paths to ".gitignore".
- Fix THE bug: User_profile_photo was not showing after signUp. - Update file-endpoints (lots of changes).
Update more endpoints in the FrontEnd.
Update buttons in "user-settings".
Various optimizations (see details). - Optimize SignUp-handling. - Prepare Controllers' GET for profile-access. - Add test css-code in footer (currently commented). - Code cleanup.
New feature: "User-profile".
Add user-following-stats in "user-profile".
- Fix error-messages not-showing. - Update signIn-validators. - Add "My profile" in userNavBar.
Fix user_profile_photos not showing in "Network".
Enable "Visit Profile" in "Network".

New feature and optimizations (see details). - New feature: Allow the admin to check and edit users-data! - Improve userId-handling in "user-info" and "user-profile". - Add logger in java-classes. - Update "README.md". - Code cleanup.
Add User-search-query in "UserRepository".
- Add BackEnd for User-search. - Update "getAllRelated"-query in "UserRepository".
Update BackEnd for user-search.

- Keep admin's navBar when the admin visits the user's info-page. - Make the "Connect Button" in user-profile to show only when the loggedIn user is someone else than the one having that profile. - Add also a "Message" button in user-profile (again with conditional showing), it does nothing yet.
"USE HTTPS" - in progress (yet disabled).
- Show the "Received" & "Sent" requests in "Network", only to the signedIn user. - Allow the "ADMIN" to have access to users' network and posts. - Code cleanup.
- FrontEnd for User-search done! - Added authorization-control for user-search in the BackEnd. - Add new "UsersInteractionService" which handled friendRequests and -in the future- messages.
- Improve user's navigation. - Code cleanup.
- Handle case when no user was found with search, in "Network". - Add "warning()" in "AlertService".
- Avoid listing "admin-user" in user-search. - Code cleanup.
Update contact-info in footer.
- New UI for "user-info" & "user-settings". Picture-update was moved to "user-info". - Typescript-code-fix: user-info not showing and profilePicture not updating.
- Optimize "Network"-UI, add messages (per-user-role) for no-connection-data.
The Admin can now extract some users-data to XML.
- Fix bug: "Could not write JSON: Infinite recursion (StackOverFlow)" - Resolve DataBase-conflicts.
Enable profile_pictures in posts and comments.
- Add authorization-check in "user-home". - Add test code for admin-id-pages-guard in "core-routing".
- XML-extraction works for all users (except from authorization). - Update "AppInstaller.sh" to guard against angular-version-change. - Code cleanup.
Add SQL tables for "JobOffers" and "JobApplies".
- Fix Merge-Conflicts.
Fix an issue, where post-owner-photo would be displayed instead of commenter's-photo, in "home-user".
Add the ability to navigate to posters' and commenters' profiles, by clicking their profile_photo or their name.
When a user searches for others in network, exclude itself from search-results.
Add authorization-check in "messages".
Optimize User-Search-Engine to give more results.
Indent comments under posts.
Update User-Search-Bar in "Network".
Job-Offers in progress (almost done, some fixes pending).
Update Personal-Information(see details). - New UI. - Add the ability to add and delete occupation and skills. - Changed the varType of "Strength" of a skill, from "int" to "String" (DB changed).
- Add Occupation-info in profile-label-tags. - Add Connections-count in "user-profile". - Comment-out some unused icons in "user-info".
Switch back to Json in http-responses.
- Add new "keytool" commands for certificate generation. - Add "keystore.p12" & "tedCertificate.crt".
- Update "EnsureHttpsInterceptor". - Update HTTPS-settings in "application.properties".
Add authorization-check in "Notifications".
Fix "Occupation-delete-icon" still appearing after occupation-deletion.
Add "ValidatorService".
